8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19mVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=1203c979\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_5gNp5uh25c</a><br />\n<br />\n去年六月九日，一百萬人遊行反對修訂逃犯條例，遊行、集會等活動自此頻頻出現。同一時間，這一年內的公眾活動通知書制度、「限聚令」及人大常委會制訂的港區國安法，會如何影響香港的集會與遊行的自由？"},{"pid":"fa24dc4826136b74eef09764274630103eca7bd0","tid":2056070,"uid":66178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:26:59.000Z","msg":"鏗鏘集用啲音樂都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc136a40876b84bd209528e34f3507f32013ed7","tid":2056070,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T12:06:02.000Z","msg":"防疫產品的迷思<br />\n<br />\n新冠狀病毒疫情肆虐下，市面防疫產品大行其道。當中有不少聲稱能夠有效預防甚至殺死病毒的產品；有產品自稱天然同高科技，能夠吸入人體。究竟這些產品所宣稱的功效有幾準確？背後又會否有消費者不熟知的風險？<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/103320514_2992422600806802_4684110944342813976_o.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=7TunECFvPXsAX-2MqzJ&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=8d1fb9a6a13dc93bb11325facdc993f2&amp;oe=5F0DC7D9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F103320514_2992422600806802_4684110944342813976_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3D7TunECFvPXsAX-2MqzJ%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3D8d1fb9a6a13dc93bb11325facdc993f2%26oe%3D5F0DC7D9&h=abff657c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/103539766_2992422830806779_5369428545538821440_o.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=bqmdBpHpJ7oAX_Wdedk&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=be8cf7c81c727a9b240d38975c20ef5f&amp;oe=5F0B9F34\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F103539766_2992422830806779_5369428545538821440_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3Dbqm